Professional Used Clothing Supplier

Zagumi is a trusted used clothing supplier who buys and sells a wide assortment of bulk used clothing for men, women, and kids. All our used clothes are professionally sorted by well-trained employees who ensure each bale contains the appropriate amount of clothing you require. Zagumi’s team can achieve an accurate bale weight and fit around 14,000kg into a 20 ft. container or around 28,000kg into a 40 ft. container. Experienced staff can efficiently sort, categorize, and load wholesale used clothing within 7 days.

Our Range of Wholesale Used Clothing

Our used clothing is known for superior quality, fashionable styles, and a neat appearance. Take a close look at our used clothing to check the quality.

Say Yes for the Superior, No for Inferior
